description:
# 2 Screen Filer NyanFi

Keyboard operation This is the 2 screen filer of the main unit.  
It is reasonably multifunctional, image display is also good, FTP connection is also possible.  
You can customize the design and operation in detail.  
Supported language is Japanese only.  

キーボード操作主体の2画面ファイラーです。  
そこそこ多機能で、ビュアーなどもなかなか、FTP接続も可能。  
デザインや操作を細かくカスタマイズできます。
summary: NyanFi is a multifunctional dual screen filer
author: Nekomimi
